etries when present in ferromagnetic/non-magnetic\nstructures through their induced current-driven spin torques. Although we give\na short chronological overview, the main body is structured from a pedagogical\npoint of view, focusing on well-established and accepted physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Nov 2014 17:23:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-13"}
