ur algorithm is an economic procedure\nof obtaining galaxy mock catalogues down to faint magnitudes that are necessary\nto understand and interpret galaxy surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Nov 2014 19:17:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
