eptor cluster\n(CeCl6Li6Cs8)12+ embedded in a quantum mechanical embedding potential of the\nhost. The calculations provide interpretations of unexplained experimental\nobservations as due to higher energy IVCT absorptions, and allow reinterpreting\nothers. The existence of another IVCT emission of lower energy, at around\n14000-16000 cm-1 less than the 5dt2g emission, is also predicted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Nov 2014 11:51:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2014 11:58:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
