derations as commonly used in\nflavor model building. Still, our formulae can be used to build up a flavor\nmodel that predicts the observed hierarchies in the masses---the mixing follows\nthen from the procedure which is developed in this work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Nov 2014 14:20:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Jan 2015 09:18:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-02"}
